How to put React and Redux together

-Hard coded list of Songs
  -Title and Length

-Have a Select button for each Song
  -When selected, show Details for that Song on one side of the screen

-When a user selects a different Song, show Details for that Song


COMPONENT STRUCTURE
-React Side
1. SongList: list of Songs that is an array of objects
  -Title and Length
  -Render out the list of Songs

2. SongDetail: Displays the Song Title and Length of given Song


REACT-REDUX
-Install Redux to the new app
-Also install React-Redux
React-Redux: 3rd library to use so that React and Redux can talk to each other

React --->  React-Redux --->  Redux
      <---   Gets React <---
            and Redux to
            work together
